record2TTree.cxx converts FOM binary output to a ttree, calculating a few metrics at the same time.
example compilation
g++ -g -std=c++11 -O3 -o Record2TTree -I<FOM_INSTALL_DIR>/include -L<FOM_INSTALL_DIR>/lib -lFOMUtils $(root-config --cflags --ldflags) -L$(root-config --libdir) - -lCore -lTree -lRIO -lrt record2TTree.cxx
